      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "3.认真区分，选字填空。",
        "bbox": [
          0.35793136549076077,
          0.12264984227129337,
          0.5167986561075114,
          0.14889589905362777
        ],
        "order": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_17",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(2)春风吹来，杏花开了。",
        "bbox": [
          0.6795056395488361,
          0.18893796004206098,
          0.9416846652267818,
          0.2501787592008412
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(1)五颜六色的（ )球飞上了天空。",
        "bbox": [
          0.3747300215982721,
          0.21720294426919032,
          0.6282697384209264,
          0.2432807570977918
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(2)夏天，孩子们非常喜欢喝（ ）水。",
        "bbox": [
          0.37449004079673626,
          0.25034700315457414,
          0.6341492680585553,
          0.2762565720294427
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "6.把儿歌补充完整。 一九二九 三九四九 7 五九六九， 看柳， 七九 雁来， 九九加一九，耕牛 O",
        "bbox": [
          0.6645068394528437,
          0.2550578338590957,
          0.8862491000719942,
          0.44769716088328076
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "1.把字和读音连一连。",
        "bbox": [
          0.05243580513558915,
          0.25859095688748684,
          0.2027837772978162,
          0.2848370136698212
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(3)老师（ )领孩子们去海边。 （4）他（ )着一副眼镜，看起来很 斯文。",
        "bbox": [
          0.37281017518598514,
          0.3445636172450053,
          0.6352291816654667,
          0.4360883280757098
        ],
        "order": 14
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "4.用部首查字法查字典，并完成练习。",
        "bbox": [
          0.35769138468922484,
          0.44382754994742374,
          0.611351091912647,
          0.4697371188222923
        ],
        "order": 15
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_19",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "亲子阅读",
        "bbox": [
          0.6946244300455964,
          0.46603575184016827,
          0.7709383249340053,
          0.4905993690851735
        ],
        "order": 16
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_20",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "名著推荐：《小巴掌童话百篇》",
        "bbox": [
          0.6960643148548116,
          0.5028811777076762,
          0.894528437724982,
          0.5294637223974763
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_21",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "推荐理由：本书中的童 话童趣盎然，语言优美。故 事篇幅短小，却非常生动， 富有内涵哲理，用童话的方 式教育、引导、启迪我们，让 我们在感受快乐的同时，学会自我思考。 小巴掌童话既是给我们的精神食粮，更是 一场心理的馈赠。我们快来一起读一 读吧！",
        "bbox": [
          0.6642668586513079,
          0.5358569926393271,
          0.8497720182385409,
          0.6943427970557308
        ],
        "order": 19
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_22",
        "observed_type": "image_body",
        "canon_role": "picture",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
          0.857571394288457,
          0.5373711882229233,
