          0.7012407991587802
        ],
        "order": 20
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "2.把下面的词语补充完整，再完成练习。 ( ）开雾散 ( ）天雪地 鹅（ ）大雪 （ )闪雷鸣 ( ）雨交加 寒（ ）刺骨",
        "bbox": [
          0.05087592992560595,
          0.66136698212408,
          0.32145428365730744,
          0.7856992639327024
        ],
        "order": 21
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3341_15",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "5.你能仿照例子，把下面的句子写得更有 趣吗？ 例：仰望天空，星星在闪烁。 仰望天空，星星在眨眼晴。",
